{"tid":543333,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"做人好悶","createTime":"2018-01-28T11:25:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T11:47:36.000Z","uid":51114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"01b88261fa5b1f981ac1eab3e341ae65051787c6","tid":543333,"uid":51114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T11:25:08.000Z","msg":"人又冇 錢又冇<br />\n<br />\n每日番工放工<br />\n<br />\n今日星期日放假<br />\n<br />\n連英超都冇<br />\n<br />\n睇波係我專一鍾意既野<br />\n<br />\n訓係鋪床度冇野好做<br />\n<br />\n諗諗下<br />\n<br />\n人生為乜 <br />\n<br />\n好想針"},{"pid":"ab880a6385998c8d052c35d15cb3f5b4cff12d8a","tid":543333,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T11:26:09.000Z","msg":"啱啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ba20e438ed024f931dc460224ed3e0f1e30fd2","tid":543333,"uid":163849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T11:28:04.000Z","msg":"有時做人就係因為將想要既野無限放大<br />\n<br />\n結果望唔到其實身邊有好多美好既事<br />\n<br />\n有時候可以靜下 思考下 欣賞下<br />\n<br />\n都係一件好事黎 唔好諗得咁灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"335d7778c5ae97268a34245f1b893f75895ac16b","tid":543333,"uid":119783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T11:35:07.000Z","msg":"跟風屠龍"},{"pid":"b50486fe5cfcda47ef1934c83b221ab5b3375882","tid":543333,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T11:47:36.000Z","msg":"咪撚再講啦 屌你老母<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}